She stopped shaking and layed on the table, not moving.  She could 
feel herself breathing, but she couldn't talk or open her eyes.  She 
could hear the sounds that were around her, but not respond to them.  
Her body felt heavy and weak. She tried to move but couldn't.  She 
felt the cold table under her.  She was starting to wonder is she 
would ever have control over her body again. Or if she was really 
alive or in the inferno getting ready to spend eternity in a 
nightmare.
